":118481,"uid":30478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T06:01:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/h-w6wcIPHN0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fh-w6wcIPHN0&d=TytWRGNO3s0Eety5H3eok%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=f9e3068b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/h-w6wcIPHN0</a></blockquote><br />\nof course i know the answer. that's why i conduct this experiment.<br />\nit's fun, huh?</blockquote><br />\n咁頭皮絕跡，頭髮靚得出色呢？<br />\n其實啲對白好似，好易搞錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n喺我心目中, &quot;頭皮? NO WAY&quot;呢句野對廣告入面既代言人係有非常強既關聯性<br />\n而當年呢個廣告之紅係對好多人有好深印象。當時有好多人扮佢。<br />\n<br />\n所以記得&quot;頭皮? NO WAY&quot;呢句野既人應該係會聯想到同一個廣告,只係某D資訊可能會唔同, 所以我先做呢個實驗。<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 真係純學術原因, 我想知你幾歲? 因為你或其他人可能太後生, 對嗰個廣告既印象冇我想像中咁深, 影響呢個實驗既結果。唔方便既可以唔答。"},{"pid":"8e410b78a3a42231e8743553c0324368ebd8d084","tid":118481,"uid":726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T06:01:51.000Z","msg":"rejoice"},{"pid":"b57212b77a286d0e0c02253342a91ade39fb21e1","tid":118481,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T06:04:42.000Z","msg":"head and shoulders"},{"pid":"77a2369e0bc57a6339b9ece0f2e9eda89177c8e4","tid":118481,"uid":30478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T06:07:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/h-w6wcIPHN0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fh-w6wcIPHN0&d=TytWRGNO3s0Eety5H3eok%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=f9e3068b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/h-w6wcIPHN0</a></blockquote><br />\nof course i know the answer. that's why i conduct this experiment.<br />\nit's fun, huh?</blockquote><br />\n証明咩？<br />\n証明好多人會撈亂同類型野？</blockquote><br />\n撈亂就好閒<br />\n但係如果好多人實牙實齒咁答錯同一個答案, 就幾有趣<br />\n<br />\nBTW我係由Communication層面出發去睇呢件事"},{"pid":"fd9f670152f79848721fe5ab6ebdc03c9b3fcee9","tid":1