/>\n當年屋企窮, 老豆凌晨帶我去住貴樓既親戚屋企睇<br />\n呢個回憶都幾好"},{"pid":"a943d6989175d1d449f1df24009c248a3f172cd9","tid":118481,"uid":30478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T06:42:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/h-w6wcIPHN0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fh-w6wcIPHN0&d=TytWRGNO3s0Eety5H3eok%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=f9e3068b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/h-w6wcIPHN0</a></blockquote><br />\nof course i know the answer. that's why i conduct this experiment.<br />\nit's fun, huh?</blockquote><br />\n証明咩？<br />\n証明好多人會撈亂同類型野？</blockquote><br />\n撈亂就好閒<br />\n但係如果好多人實牙實齒咁答錯同一個答案, 就幾有趣<br />\n<br />\nBTW我係由Communication層面出發去睇呢件事</blockquote><br />\n好似幾好玩，仲有冇多啲例子？<br />\n<br />\nBtw 我好記得係張德培同rejoice，我80後前段</blockquote><br />\n未諗到<br />\n<br />\n呢個實驗我係喺舊公司做過一次, 咁岩拎返上黎玩唧"},{"pid":"622f94930d8fad728928ab1ae3e437d55e17faf2","tid":118481,"uid":30478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T06:44:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>答張德培既應該都係80後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 我90後都答得出</blockquote><br />\n90後前期既應該當年應該有幾歲<br />\n所以應該仲有幾深印象<br />\n當年廣告一出, 好多人扮<br />\n<br />\n1996年既廣告, 我諗太後生既應該會直接記錯以為我講緊D 2000年打後既(例如有人話蔡依林王力宏, 我CHECK過, 唔係講頭皮NO WAY)"},{"pid":"332254ebea704e6796ef9ecac23de5d2a86a149e","tid":118481,"uid":43678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T07:02:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>答張德培既應該都係80後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 我90後都答得出</blockquote><br />\n90後前期既應該當年應該有幾歲<br />\n所以應該仲有幾深印象<br />\n當年廣告一出, 好多人扮<br />\n<br />\n1996年既廣告, 我諗太後生既應該會直接記錯以為我講緊D 2000年打後既(例如有人話蔡依林王力宏, 我CHECK過, 唔係講頭皮NO WAY)</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n同埋句對白套落返2000年後就好老土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc2f6ecd9d51407b08958478df43ed6aced4f6d"